B.B1=new A.jE("Aosta India Private Limited","Software Engineer","Apr 2024 - Present","Currently working as a Full-Stack Developer at Aosta India Private Limited, where I design and develop scalable mobile and web applications with a strong focus on performance, usability, and real-time data handling.I have been actively involved in building healthcare-based systems, particularly EMR (Electronic Medical Records) applications, where I worked on features like patient management, prescription modules, scan notes handling, and dynamic medical data rendering.On the frontend, I use Flutter to develop responsive and high-performance cross-platform applications, ensuring smooth UI/UX and optimized state management. I have implemented complex UI components such as dynamic forms, real-time suggestions, and interactive dashboards.On the backend, I work with Node.js and SQL-based systems to build APIs, handle authentication, and manage large-scale data efficiently. I have experience integrating REST APIs, handling JSON/XML responses, and optimizing database queries using MySQL and MongoDB.I have also worked on file handling features such as uploading and retrieving medical images and documents securely from server paths, ensuring proper storage and access control.Additionally, I explore AI and Prompt Engineering techniques to enhance application capabilities, including intelligent suggestions, automation, and improving user interaction within the system.Throughout my work, I focus on writing clean, maintainable code and collaborating effectively with teams to deliver reliable and scalable solutions.",B.Dy,!0)
